{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6ed6ec0c5a","title":"大字报——五人小组不能成为挡箭牌","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（一）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"875492c9b9","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"6ed6ec0c5a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f61eadb28f","name":"太原工学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e40a10f467","type":"title","text":"大字报——五人小组不能成为挡箭牌","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6ed6ec0c5a"},{"id":"095cef53cd","type":"authors","text":"太原工学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6ed6ec0c5a"},{"id":"e8331c78fd","type":"paragraph","text":"我们反对党委石书记的问题解答，他说肃反的错误由五人小组来负责，我们认为“五人小组”不能逃避责任，包庇黄克，除二个被惩的人之外，其他三人应按情节轻重分别予以处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6ed6ec0c5a"},{"id":"bd5d1df1d4","type":"paragraph","text":"我们坚决支持老师和老大哥们的要求，公审违犯国法、盗窃国家建设资金，破坏党纪的黄克，并对党委的包庇态度提出抗议。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6ed6ec0c5a"},{"id":"20080ee492","type":"paragraph","text":" 太原工学院（制6104一大群人）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6ed6ec0c5a"}],"page":{"id":"538e8c2a88","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6ed6ec0c5a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}